FBIS4-18289 "drweu064aa_94002" FBIS-WEU-94-000 Daily Report 1 Apr 1994 NATO Welcomes April Membership in PfP for Russia NATO Welcomes April Membership in PfP for Russia AU0104132394 Paris AFP in English 1253 GMT 1 Apr 94 AU0104132394 Paris AFP English BFN [Text] Brussels, April 1, (AFP) -- NATO officials Friday [1 April] welcomed Russia's assurances that it would join the Western security body's Partnership for Peace [PfP] program later this month as planned, after reports that there could be a delay. "Of course we welcome Russia's signing of Partnership for Peace, as we were expecting it to do by the end of April," said an official from the North Atlantic Treaty Organisation.
